1
00:00:08,975 --> 00:00:11,375
l have told you in the beginning

2
00:00:11,578 --> 00:00:13,239
...you are a bad guy but l am a cop

3
00:00:13,546 --> 00:00:15,571
l always treat you

4
00:00:15,849 --> 00:00:18,409
...as my son

5
00:00:18,618 --> 00:00:20,643
l only want to be a cop

6
00:00:20,854 --> 00:00:22,116
My son Jason knows

7
00:00:22,322 --> 00:00:25,485
...how good l am to you

8
00:00:26,726 --> 00:00:28,193
Don`t use Jason to blackmail me

9
00:00:29,562 --> 00:00:32,690
To be honest, l won`t

10
00:00:32,899 --> 00:00:34,890
...live long enough to protect you

11
00:00:35,101 --> 00:00:40,129
Jason, do you have the tape?

12
00:00:43,810 --> 00:00:46,472
Yes, l have it

13
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:52,916
You are under my control

14
00:01:07,867 --> 00:01:11,428
Son, l know who killed you

15
00:01:12,338 --> 00:01:14,670
l will revenge your death

16
00:02:42,929 --> 00:02:44,863
Mom, are you feeling better now?

17
00:02:46,766 --> 00:02:48,393
l feel much relieved now

18
00:02:48,902 --> 00:02:50,199
...that you have grown up

19
00:02:52,405 --> 00:02:55,067
Mom, what is wrong with my brother?

20
00:02:55,742 --> 00:02:57,369
No, nothing

21
00:02:58,344 --> 00:03:00,471
Tell me what`s wrong

22
00:03:03,449 --> 00:03:04,882
l`ll tell you

23
00:03:05,485 --> 00:03:07,009
...but don`t tell anybody else

24
00:03:07,353 --> 00:03:08,377
l won`t

25
00:03:08,788 --> 00:03:09,846
0ne night

26
00:03:10,123 --> 00:03:12,114
...your brother brought a man home

27
00:03:12,325 --> 00:03:14,589
...l went to buy them food

28
00:03:14,894 --> 00:03:17,692
When l was downstairs
l heard a gunshot

29
00:03:18,031 --> 00:03:20,499
l went back home

30
00:03:21,301 --> 00:03:24,498
l saw your brother holding a gun
in his hand

31
00:03:24,704 --> 00:03:26,194
He has killed the man!

32
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:29,403
Mom, we have to report this
to the police

33
00:03:29,576 --> 00:03:30,338
No, we can`t do that

34
00:03:30,543 --> 00:03:32,511
You brother said it will ruin him

35
00:03:32,679 --> 00:03:34,613
Who`s that man?

36
00:03:35,181 --> 00:03:36,671
That man`s called...

37
00:03:36,883 --> 00:03:38,976
son...son

38
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,411
Jason?

39
00:03:40,954 --> 00:03:41,613
Who`s he?

40
00:03:41,821 --> 00:03:43,652
Son of a triad society boss

41
00:03:43,856 --> 00:03:45,915
So what should we do?

42
00:03:46,459 --> 00:03:47,187
We are in big trouble!

43
00:03:47,393 --> 00:03:49,258
Mom, l will talk to Madam. We will
think of something

44
00:03:50,263 --> 00:03:52,629
What`s the matter?

45
00:03:53,433 --> 00:03:54,331
Mom, don`t be afraid!

46
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:55,660
l`ll go and take a look

47
00:03:55,902 --> 00:03:56,630
Quick

48
00:03:56,803 --> 00:03:58,862
Mom, stay calm

49
00:05:40,473 --> 00:05:46,434
What`s the matter? Get the phone?

50
00:05:46,646 --> 00:05:48,705
Phone, phone, phone

51
00:05:52,785 --> 00:05:53,979
Quick

52
00:06:00,059 --> 00:06:00,684
Hey

53
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:03,124
Hey, brother, there is someone
in our house

54
00:06:03,296 --> 00:06:05,958
What? Don`t open the door

55
00:06:06,366 --> 00:06:08,095
BiBi, dial 999

56
00:06:12,271 --> 00:06:13,295
Call the police

57
00:07:02,522 --> 00:07:03,454
What`s happened?

58
00:07:04,056 --> 00:07:04,784
Sir, a fire has broken out

59
00:07:04,991 --> 00:07:05,423
Which unit?

60
00:07:05,591 --> 00:07:06,421
13th floor

61
00:07:08,795 --> 00:07:25,577
Mom, BiBi, Mom, BiBi. Let me in

62
00:07:26,045 --> 00:07:27,569
You can`t go in. lt`s too dangerous

63
00:07:27,814 --> 00:07:30,009
Calm down

64
00:09:08,014 --> 00:09:11,074
Hon, why do l have to do that?

65
00:09:11,450 --> 00:09:14,851
My son was burnt into
a piece of black coal

66
00:09:15,054 --> 00:09:18,319
There was a bullet inside his body

67
00:09:18,958 --> 00:09:22,826
l can`t sleep after his death

68
00:09:23,062 --> 00:09:24,222
lt is fair that...

69
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:26,955
Someone should suffer
the same pain as l have

70
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,163
Fatso, what do you want?

71
00:09:30,303 --> 00:09:32,271
l like your toughness

72
00:09:32,471 --> 00:09:33,233
l`ll ask you to accompany me

73
00:09:33,472 --> 00:09:34,632
...should there be an accident

74
00:10:39,238 --> 00:10:42,469
Damn you. Let me get out of the car

75
00:11:22,548 --> 00:11:23,776
Are you Piano?

76
00:11:24,083 --> 00:11:25,015
Yes, Auntie

77
00:11:25,217 --> 00:11:26,844
David often talks about you

78
00:11:27,053 --> 00:11:29,317
l am on vacation so l`ve
come to see you

79
00:11:30,256 --> 00:11:32,656
Yes, l long to meet you

80
00:11:32,858 --> 00:11:35,850
l am very happy to meet you today

81
00:11:36,095 --> 00:11:37,824
A fire has broken out in a unit at

82
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,657
...Kwun Tong 18 Hong Lee Road
13th floor

83
00:11:39,865 --> 00:11:40,490
Do you want to watch TV?

84
00:11:40,666 --> 00:11:41,530
Yes

85
00:11:42,001 --> 00:11:42,933
l turn it louder

86
00:11:43,569 --> 00:11:46,333
The police suspects arson

87
00:11:48,174 --> 00:11:49,801
We also have Hong Kong news here

88
00:11:50,176 --> 00:11:52,235
...only delayed

89
00:11:55,347 --> 00:11:58,214
lt`s impossible. lt can`t be real

90
00:12:01,921 --> 00:12:03,548
They are my friends

91
00:12:03,989 --> 00:12:05,422
What`s happened?

92
00:12:05,558 --> 00:12:07,788
Auntie, l have to go now

93
00:12:08,561 --> 00:12:10,085
Piano, aren`t you staying here?

94
00:12:10,296 --> 00:12:11,263
l have to return to Hong Kong

95
00:12:23,476 --> 00:12:26,411
Come in, Hon

96
00:12:35,087 --> 00:12:35,917
What`s the matter, Madam?

97
00:12:37,289 --> 00:12:38,415
Why do you still come back to the office

98
00:12:40,226 --> 00:12:41,284
Why shouldn`t l?

99
00:12:42,194 --> 00:12:43,661
l think you need a rest

100
00:12:45,197 --> 00:12:47,495
l am okay, Madam. l don`t need a rest

101
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:51,198
l won`t let an emotionally
unstable person

102
00:12:51,437 --> 00:12:53,302
...walking around on the street
with a gun

103
00:12:56,041 --> 00:12:58,236
Madam, l am okay

104
00:12:58,444 --> 00:12:59,536
Why must l take leave?

105
00:13:01,881 --> 00:13:04,577
Hand in your gun and your pass

106
00:13:05,017 --> 00:13:06,450
Go and see the psychologist

107
00:13:06,685 --> 00:13:08,414
lf he says you are fine

108
00:13:08,654 --> 00:13:10,121
...then l`ll let you come back
to work at once

109
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:13,157
lt`s not fair

110
00:13:13,659 --> 00:13:14,785
lt`s an order

111
00:13:35,481 --> 00:13:37,005
Everyone-get back to work

112
00:14:00,105 --> 00:14:01,697
Mr. Hon, take it easy! Don`t feel so bad

113
00:14:02,708 --> 00:14:06,838
Mom, BiBi, l will revenge your death

114
00:14:58,964 --> 00:15:01,524
So, are you feeling depressed?

115
00:15:02,067 --> 00:15:03,694
Take it easy!

116
00:15:04,136 --> 00:15:07,333
Tonight you will sleep soundly

117
00:15:07,973 --> 00:15:09,372
0f course l will sleep well

118
00:15:10,309 --> 00:15:11,799
l hope you do too

119
00:15:12,044 --> 00:15:13,477
...so that you can dream of your son

120
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:16,946
Yes, l have dreamed of my son

121
00:15:17,149 --> 00:15:18,582
My son told me that

122
00:15:18,784 --> 00:15:21,252
...you will not have any heirs

123
00:15:22,087 --> 00:15:23,145
That`s good

124
00:15:23,656 --> 00:15:26,056
Please tell your son tonight that

125
00:15:26,458 --> 00:15:28,187
...his dad will come to see him
very soon

126
00:15:28,827 --> 00:15:31,022
Fine. And when l was there

127
00:15:31,230 --> 00:15:34,358
...l would also tell your mother
and sister that

128
00:15:34,566 --> 00:15:36,500
...they would have their family
reunion very soon

129
00:15:37,503 --> 00:15:38,595
May your wish come true!

130
00:16:28,487 --> 00:16:29,283
Come in

131
00:16:30,389 --> 00:16:31,583
Have you finished your work?

132
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:37,820
What`s the matter? You look unhappy

133
00:16:38,163 --> 00:16:38,993
How do you know?

134
00:16:39,932 --> 00:16:41,058
J ust by looking at you

135
00:16:42,401 --> 00:16:44,369
Hon lost his temper today

136
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:46,330
...when l asked him to take leave

137
00:16:47,473 --> 00:16:48,371
Why?

138
00:16:49,975 --> 00:16:50,532
You know his mother and BiBi

139
00:16:50,743 --> 00:16:52,643
...had just passed away

140
00:16:52,845 --> 00:16:54,437
l was afraid he was
emotionally unstable

141
00:16:54,646 --> 00:16:57,308
...so l asked him to take leave

142
00:16:58,050 --> 00:16:59,483
He has too much on his mind

143
00:17:03,956 --> 00:17:05,719
Don`t worry too much

144
00:17:06,291 --> 00:17:08,782
l`ll dine with you tonight

145
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:10,021
Great

146
00:17:11,430 --> 00:17:12,988
Relax

147
00:17:23,075 --> 00:17:24,565
Madam, these were

148
00:17:24,777 --> 00:17:26,005
...Lynn`s tapes

149
00:17:27,279 --> 00:17:28,007
Thank you

150
00:18:26,605 --> 00:18:27,003
What`s the matter?

151
00:18:27,172 --> 00:18:27,501
Police

152
00:18:27,573 --> 00:18:28,597
We`re the Police

153
00:18:30,375 --> 00:18:33,606
Mister, l am Ann Wong, SP of the 0CTB

154
00:18:34,246 --> 00:18:37,306
l have heard of you for a long time

155
00:18:37,583 --> 00:18:39,278
l did not expect you to be
so good looking

156
00:18:39,485 --> 00:18:41,248
Cut the crap. Please go back
to the station with us

157
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:43,044
l need to ask you some questions

158
00:18:43,255 --> 00:18:44,984
...concerning the murder
of the female reporter

159
00:18:46,492 --> 00:18:48,460
What`s your relationship with Hon Gin?

160
00:18:49,261 --> 00:18:52,321
Hon Gin, he`s a cop

161
00:18:52,564 --> 00:18:53,861
l have no relationship whatsoever
with cops

162
00:18:55,334 --> 00:18:57,734
Fatso, Madam is asking you a question

163
00:18:58,270 --> 00:18:59,498
Stop cracking jokes!

164
00:19:00,639 --> 00:19:03,073
Sir, don`t shout at me

165
00:19:03,275 --> 00:19:05,937
l am old-l can`t stand loud noises!

166
00:19:07,346 --> 00:19:09,041
Lynn was a female reporter from CBN

167
00:19:09,314 --> 00:19:10,645
She shot you dining with Hon Gin

168
00:19:10,883 --> 00:19:13,716
...in a restaurant in Kowloon City

169
00:19:14,019 --> 00:19:15,008
What were you talking about?

170
00:19:15,487 --> 00:19:20,049
l remember that incident now
that you mention it

171
00:19:20,125 --> 00:19:21,456
That night...

172
00:19:21,693 --> 00:19:23,490
They pointed their cameras at me

173
00:19:23,695 --> 00:19:26,186
Well, Madam, there are

174
00:19:26,431 --> 00:19:27,227
...many restaurants in that mansion

175
00:19:27,432 --> 00:19:30,401
How can you say l dined with Hon?

176
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:32,728
Don`t try to fool us Fatso

177
00:19:33,005 --> 00:19:33,494
Everybody knows that...

178
00:19:33,705 --> 00:19:35,297
...you own all the restaurants
in that building

179
00:19:36,141 --> 00:19:38,575
Yes, l own all the restaurants

180
00:19:38,777 --> 00:19:40,267
Can l refuse Hon

181
00:19:40,479 --> 00:19:44,438
...to dine in one of them?

182
00:19:44,783 --> 00:19:47,343
Fatso, we just want to know

183
00:19:47,553 --> 00:19:49,521
...if you meet with Hon Gin frequently

184
00:19:49,721 --> 00:19:52,121
Madam, who do you think l am
a rookie?

185
00:19:52,324 --> 00:19:56,488
Even if l am, l won`t say so

186
00:19:58,997 --> 00:20:00,794
He`s going around in circles

187
00:20:01,066 --> 00:20:03,125
The bosses of triad societies
are like that

188
00:20:03,769 --> 00:20:05,532
But Madam, do you suspect
our Boss...?

189
00:20:05,938 --> 00:20:08,429
There are the tapes and
material evidence

190
00:20:08,774 --> 00:20:10,071
...on quite a few murders to which
l can not be blind

191
00:20:10,309 --> 00:20:12,300
But you will get married two days later

192
00:20:12,477 --> 00:20:13,671
...let us handle the case

193
00:20:13,879 --> 00:20:14,903
Yes, let us handle it

194
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:15,910
Yeah

195
00:20:16,548 --> 00:20:19,176
Lock him up for 24 hours
then discharge him

196
00:20:19,384 --> 00:20:19,975
...and follow him around the clock

197
00:20:20,152 --> 00:20:21,141
0kay, we will

198
00:21:52,811 --> 00:22:00,809
lnspector, why are you here?

199
00:22:01,353 --> 00:22:02,980
l haven`t sold guns for a long time

200
00:22:03,488 --> 00:22:06,582
Whatever happened has
nothing to do with me

201
00:22:06,925 --> 00:22:08,586
Don`t lie to me

202
00:22:09,127 --> 00:22:10,856
l know what you have been doing

203
00:22:11,330 --> 00:22:13,628
lf so, arrest me!

204
00:22:15,167 --> 00:22:16,395
l need a gun

205
00:22:18,437 --> 00:22:19,927
Are you kidding?

206
00:22:20,238 --> 00:22:22,001
A cop wants to buy a gun from me?

207
00:22:23,208 --> 00:22:25,676
l am not a cop anymore
and l need a gun

208
00:22:25,911 --> 00:22:29,278
Sir, aren`t you holding a gun
in your hand?

209
00:22:29,514 --> 00:22:31,072
l need one more

210
00:22:31,650 --> 00:22:32,810
Do you understand me?

211
00:22:33,051 --> 00:22:35,417
Yes, yes

212
00:26:40,432 --> 00:26:42,900
Little Dog, what have you got?

213
00:26:43,101 --> 00:26:43,760
The cop has taken our bait

214
00:26:44,002 --> 00:26:45,492
We have cornered him into a room

215
00:26:45,704 --> 00:26:47,228
He`s got two guns

216
00:26:47,572 --> 00:26:48,561
l know he will come one day

217
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:50,173
Why would he need another gun?

218
00:26:50,508 --> 00:26:52,032
Take him alive

219
00:26:52,243 --> 00:26:53,870
Shoot him on sight and then

220
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:55,910
...throw his dead body in the
reclamation area

221
00:26:56,815 --> 00:26:59,579
0h no, let me take a look at his corpse

222
00:26:59,784 --> 00:27:00,978
...before you dispose of it

223
00:27:04,889 --> 00:27:05,981
Now you can see me

224
00:27:06,825 --> 00:27:09,760
Hon, this is a public place

225
00:27:15,166 --> 00:27:17,691
Fatso, don`t bullshit me!

226
00:27:19,904 --> 00:27:21,565
l`ll give you 3 million to get away
from Hong Kong

227
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:23,173
l guarantee you will be safe

228
00:27:24,976 --> 00:27:26,307
You think too highly of me

229
00:27:27,078 --> 00:27:30,172
l only want justice to be done

230
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,408
What are you doing?

231
00:27:33,652 --> 00:27:34,914
Waiting for ``Sheung Tau``!

232
00:27:35,954 --> 00:27:37,148
What`s ``Sheung Tau``?

233
00:27:38,056 --> 00:27:38,681
You know

234
00:27:38,923 --> 00:27:41,653
...the elderly use a comb
to brush the hair!

235
00:27:43,595 --> 00:27:45,620
You probably can`t understand this

236
00:27:47,265 --> 00:27:49,028
Aren`t you staying with your boys?

237
00:27:49,467 --> 00:27:51,662
No, l am now having a drink

238
00:27:51,870 --> 00:27:54,338
...with Sir Chow

239
00:27:54,973 --> 00:27:56,338
Quick. Hang up the phone!

240
00:27:56,541 --> 00:27:57,473
You are so long.winded!

241
00:27:57,709 --> 00:27:58,698
Do you hear that?

242
00:27:59,644 --> 00:28:00,804
Tell her to shut up

243
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:03,377
Go and take a bath

244
00:28:03,615 --> 00:28:06,209
We don`t have much time

245
00:28:06,418 --> 00:28:07,282
Quick

246
00:28:07,652 --> 00:28:10,917
Do you hear that? l`ll go now, bye

247
00:28:14,059 --> 00:28:15,424
You are a grown.up now

248
00:28:16,761 --> 00:28:18,456
Cheers

249
00:28:20,699 --> 00:28:22,098
Don`t yell

250
00:28:22,333 --> 00:28:23,391
You have so many ideas

251
00:28:23,601 --> 00:28:28,595
My dear cousin, you better be quick

252
00:28:28,807 --> 00:28:29,603
Wear your shoes and pajamas...

253
00:28:29,841 --> 00:28:31,331
And have your hair combed

254
00:28:38,616 --> 00:28:39,173
Hey

255
00:28:39,417 --> 00:28:40,611
Madam, this is Hon speaking

256
00:28:40,785 --> 00:28:41,547
Wait

257
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:43,444
l have to talk to you

258
00:28:44,489 --> 00:28:45,683
What`s wrong?

259
00:28:45,857 --> 00:28:47,347
l have to talk to you

260
00:28:47,525 --> 00:28:48,549
l`ll wait for you downstairs

261
00:28:48,793 --> 00:28:52,593
Please come down by yourself
and don`t tell anyone

262
00:28:53,098 --> 00:28:54,122
l can see you now

263
00:28:54,999 --> 00:28:56,091
l`ll come down at once

264
00:29:03,508 --> 00:29:04,770
l am going out for a while

265
00:29:09,681 --> 00:29:10,340
Hey, Stone

266
00:29:10,548 --> 00:29:12,641
...tomorrow you will no longer
be a bachelor

267
00:29:12,851 --> 00:29:14,318
Cheers

268
00:29:14,519 --> 00:29:16,282
Cheers

269
00:29:17,021 --> 00:29:21,424
Someone must be on duty

270
00:29:21,659 --> 00:29:23,593
Stone, take it easy

271
00:29:23,928 --> 00:29:26,488
Big Wei, Big Guy, Frankie and Ah Sun

272
00:29:26,698 --> 00:29:27,756
...take turns to stand on guard

273
00:29:27,966 --> 00:29:30,526
We are free today

274
00:29:32,737 --> 00:29:33,897
Tonight is your last night as a bachelor

275
00:29:34,105 --> 00:29:36,539
We`re going to have a great time!

276
00:29:39,410 --> 00:29:40,172
Do you still remember

277
00:29:40,378 --> 00:29:41,675
...Madam Ann?

278
00:29:41,846 --> 00:29:43,211
We do

279
00:29:43,414 --> 00:29:44,381
