01:01:43,933 --> 01:01:45,525
What`s so bad about the SDU?

563
01:01:45,968 --> 01:01:47,230
What is so good about being
a member of the SDU?

564
01:01:47,403 --> 01:01:49,701
You can`t get a wife

565
01:01:49,772 --> 01:01:51,637
Hey, Ann...

566
01:01:53,910 --> 01:01:56,037
My dad is like a stone

567
01:01:56,245 --> 01:01:57,678
l hope you don`t mind him

568
01:01:58,214 --> 01:01:59,613
l`ll kiss you for him

569
01:02:00,950 --> 01:02:02,144
This bouquet is for you

570
01:02:02,318 --> 01:02:04,183
Wish you get married soon!

571
01:02:04,420 --> 01:02:05,978
You still act like a kid

572
01:02:06,155 --> 01:02:07,087
...even though you are a grown.up

573
01:02:16,999 --> 01:02:19,058
The SDU will welcome you back

574
01:02:19,202 --> 01:02:21,727
...once you`ve recovered

575
01:02:22,505 --> 01:02:24,132
l can report to duty any time

576
01:02:24,440 --> 01:02:28,308
Ann is over there

577
01:02:29,545 --> 01:02:31,274
l don`t know what you`re talking about

578
01:02:31,948 --> 01:02:32,915
lf you don`t go there now

579
01:02:33,216 --> 01:02:34,706
...l will punish you run 50 lapses

580
01:02:34,917 --> 01:02:36,714
...do 100 sit.ups, and 100 push.ups

581
01:02:38,988 --> 01:02:40,012
0kay

582
01:02:40,423 --> 01:02:41,117
Then go

583
01:02:41,290 --> 01:02:41,984
Thank you

584
01:02:42,258 --> 01:02:42,952
Come on

585
01:02:43,126 --> 01:02:44,024
0kay

586
01:03:03,780 --> 01:03:05,873
Ann, l always regard you

587
01:03:06,082 --> 01:03:08,016
...as an outstanding police officer

588
01:03:08,751 --> 01:03:10,582
lt`s not easy for a woman

589
01:03:10,787 --> 01:03:12,982
...to be in your position

590
01:03:13,556 --> 01:03:14,989
l hope you will re.consider

591
01:03:15,224 --> 01:03:18,284
...your resignation

592
01:03:19,562 --> 01:03:22,122
Madam, a lot of things happened

593
01:03:22,331 --> 01:03:24,196
...in my department these few months

594
01:03:25,168 --> 01:03:26,931
...especially Hon Gin`s case

595
01:03:28,004 --> 01:03:29,471
l need a break

596
01:03:32,041 --> 01:03:34,669
l am sorry about Hon Gin

597
01:03:35,211 --> 01:03:36,906
But l will feel bad...

598
01:03:37,146 --> 01:03:38,511
lf you leave the police force too

599
01:03:40,049 --> 01:03:42,108
lf l stay most probably l have to

600
01:03:42,852 --> 01:03:45,218
...see the psychiatrist everyday

601
01:03:45,421 --> 01:03:47,889
l think this is not fair to the force?

602
01:03:51,327 --> 01:03:53,852
What`s your plan?

603
01:03:54,964 --> 01:03:57,091
l plan to go back to school in the States

604
01:03:59,001 --> 01:04:02,903
Will you come back to the police force?

605
01:04:03,472 --> 01:04:05,235
lf l get my degree

606
01:04:05,408 --> 01:04:06,500
l may come back

607
01:04:07,810 --> 01:04:09,835
0kay, then

608
01:04:10,446 --> 01:04:13,108
Do you mind if l ask you
a personal question?

609
01:04:14,851 --> 01:04:16,216
Aren`t you getting married with Stone?

610
01:04:20,223 --> 01:04:21,485
He`s a good man

611
01:04:22,859 --> 01:04:24,554
l always trust your instinct

612
01:04:25,328 --> 01:04:26,192
l wish you happiness

613
01:04:26,896 --> 01:04:27,885
Thank you Madam

614
01:04:29,465 --> 01:04:32,332
l have handed in my resignation
to Madam So today

615
01:04:33,803 --> 01:04:34,667
Why?

616
01:04:36,572 --> 01:04:38,733
l want to study psychology in the States

617
01:04:39,709 --> 01:04:40,971
Aren`t we getting married?

618
01:04:42,144 --> 01:04:45,079
We can live in the States

619
01:04:45,281 --> 01:04:47,272
We can study and get married there

620
01:04:47,550 --> 01:04:50,986
What? But all my friends are here

621
01:04:51,153 --> 01:04:54,418
...Joe, Bill, they are all here

622
01:04:56,092 --> 01:04:58,424
0nly you and l are getting married

623
01:04:59,128 --> 01:05:00,356
What has that got to do with them?

624
01:05:01,330 --> 01:05:03,855
The Chinese loves a party

625
01:05:04,066 --> 01:05:06,432
lt will be more fun. Why?

626
01:05:06,636 --> 01:05:07,568
l am not happy

627
01:05:08,871 --> 01:05:09,769
Why?

628
01:05:11,807 --> 01:05:12,603
l want to leave Hong Kong

629
01:05:12,842 --> 01:05:14,366
...after all that have happened

630
01:05:14,543 --> 01:05:15,567
Do you understand me?

631
01:05:19,282 --> 01:05:24,310
What can l say if this is what you want?

632
01:05:28,190 --> 01:05:29,350
What am l supposed to do?

633
01:05:32,194 --> 01:05:33,957
You stay calm even when

634
01:05:34,163 --> 01:05:35,755
...someone points an AK 47 at you

635
01:05:35,998 --> 01:05:37,795
...but you lose your cool over a woman

636
01:05:39,135 --> 01:05:45,131
l am a gwai lo. l am different from you

637
01:05:45,408 --> 01:05:46,568
That`s right

638
01:05:47,043 --> 01:05:49,204
Ann is going to a foreign country

639
01:05:49,412 --> 01:05:50,276
...and that suits you

640
01:05:50,713 --> 01:05:55,650
lf l leave, what will happen to the boys?

641
01:05:58,187 --> 01:06:00,621
0ne day you have to retire
from the SDU

642
01:06:00,957 --> 01:06:04,017
Do yourself a favour

643
01:06:04,226 --> 01:06:06,888
Collect your pension and
go to the States

644
01:06:07,096 --> 01:06:10,224
...stay with Ann

645
01:06:11,033 --> 01:06:12,728
They are still not good enough
to take my place

646
01:06:14,937 --> 01:06:16,768
They don`t want you to leave

647
01:06:17,306 --> 01:06:19,604
But you can`t run

648
01:06:20,042 --> 01:06:22,977
...a relay all by yourself

649
01:06:23,646 --> 01:06:25,045
lt can`t be done within a short period

650
01:06:26,882 --> 01:06:29,544
Find an appropriate time to
hand over your job

651
01:06:29,752 --> 01:06:31,413
lf you don`t

652
01:06:31,620 --> 01:06:33,417
...how do you know they are not ready?

653
01:06:35,658 --> 01:06:36,989
Not for a while

654
01:06:39,095 --> 01:06:40,756
lt can never be done if you don`t try

655
01:06:43,632 --> 01:06:44,826
You are right

656
01:06:47,470 --> 01:06:50,303
Go home and take a good rest

657
01:06:51,007 --> 01:06:54,841
Tomorrow we will test new blood
Bill, please

658
01:06:55,478 --> 01:06:56,502
Thank you Sir

659
01:07:00,282 --> 01:07:02,477
Sir, how are the new blood?

660
01:07:03,753 --> 01:07:04,777
0kay

661
01:07:05,087 --> 01:07:08,022
You were like that when you first came

662
01:07:08,257 --> 01:07:10,555
Who`s going to give the lecture?

663
01:07:10,760 --> 01:07:11,590
Lucky Lun

664
01:07:11,794 --> 01:07:12,988
Forget it. You know that l don`t like
to speak in public

665
01:07:13,195 --> 01:07:14,162
Head or tail?

666
01:07:14,330 --> 01:07:16,764
Come on, don`t waste time

667
01:07:16,932 --> 01:07:17,421
Who`ll speak first?

668
01:07:17,600 --> 01:07:22,469
0K-attention!

669
01:07:23,239 --> 01:07:24,103
Now to be a member

670
01:07:24,340 --> 01:07:25,466
...of the SDU is different
from being a DJ

671
01:07:26,308 --> 01:07:27,775
Talking is secondary to action

672
01:07:28,944 --> 01:07:31,936
What l want to ask you is...

673
01:07:32,782 --> 01:07:35,114
Why do you want to join the SDU?

674
01:07:35,618 --> 01:07:37,779
We want to be the best of the best

675
01:07:37,987 --> 01:07:38,919
Louder

676
01:07:39,121 --> 01:07:41,646
We want to be the best of the best

677
01:07:41,857 --> 01:07:43,848
Now l`ll give you five minutes
to get changed

678
01:07:44,060 --> 01:07:45,550
Then we`ll do the tests in the playground

679
01:07:45,761 --> 01:07:46,887
Yes, Sir

680
01:07:49,532 --> 01:07:51,261
He is good

681
01:07:51,801 --> 01:07:53,598
Yes, he is smart!

682
01:07:53,803 --> 01:07:54,861
l am always smart

683
01:07:55,271 --> 01:07:56,295
Go

684
01:07:57,073 --> 01:08:01,032
5 minutes! We need five minutes

685
01:08:01,243 --> 01:08:02,437
...to go to the playground

686
01:08:02,645 --> 01:08:03,612
Yes Sir

687
01:08:07,249 --> 01:08:07,977
Faster

688
01:08:12,354 --> 01:08:13,082
Faster

689
01:08:13,289 --> 01:08:14,483
They are getting worse and worse

690
01:08:16,559 --> 01:08:18,823
Keep in line!

691
01:08:20,296 --> 01:08:21,388
They are worse than me
when l first joined

692
01:08:23,332 --> 01:08:24,856
Wow, see these new guys

693
01:08:25,034 --> 01:08:26,626
They are much worse than us!

694
01:08:26,869 --> 01:08:29,736
Yes, they are getting worse and worse

695
01:08:30,639 --> 01:08:33,802
Though l have no sense of direction

696
01:08:34,043 --> 01:08:35,977
...l can still run faster than them

697
01:08:36,178 --> 01:08:38,339
Do you remember that back then

698
01:08:38,614 --> 01:08:40,946
...when the instructor calls us

699
01:08:41,183 --> 01:08:42,309
...we all turn left while you turn right?

700
01:08:42,518 --> 01:08:43,610
Where are you going?

701
01:08:43,786 --> 01:08:45,447
l turned right to avoid blocking your way

702
01:08:45,654 --> 01:08:46,211
l was tying my shoe laces

703
01:08:46,455 --> 01:08:47,387
What a silly excuse!

704
01:08:47,523 --> 01:08:48,182
And then when we changed our clothes

705
01:08:48,390 --> 01:08:49,357
...in the changing room

706
01:08:49,625 --> 01:08:50,182
...he still had not come
even after we left

707
01:08:50,392 --> 01:08:50,858
That`s right

708
01:08:51,060 --> 01:08:52,493
l have to tidy the legs of my trousers

709
01:08:52,695 --> 01:08:53,719
Yes

710
01:08:54,330 --> 01:08:56,195
No. Ask his name

711
01:08:56,365 --> 01:08:57,730
Lucky Lun

712
01:08:58,634 --> 01:08:59,794
l thought you were gay

713
01:09:00,035 --> 01:09:00,501
Why?

714
01:09:00,736 --> 01:09:01,725
You were peeking at our bodies

715
01:09:01,971 --> 01:09:03,734
Jesus was strong, so l
took a look at him

716
01:09:03,973 --> 01:09:05,497
You are not that strong

717
01:09:05,741 --> 01:09:06,765
You asked me what the tests would be

718
01:09:06,976 --> 01:09:07,533
l couldn`t answer you

719
01:09:07,776 --> 01:09:09,004
We came out of the dressing room and

720
01:09:09,211 --> 01:09:11,679
...jumped into the water immediately!

721
01:09:11,947 --> 01:09:12,413
lt was cold at that time

722
01:09:12,615 --> 01:09:13,081
Yeah, very cold

723
01:09:13,315 --> 01:09:13,838
Yeah

724
01:09:14,049 --> 01:09:15,107
You haven`t tidied the legs
of your trousers

725
01:09:15,317 --> 01:09:15,681
Yeah

726
01:09:15,918 --> 01:09:16,646
John was funnier

727
01:09:16,852 --> 01:09:17,318
What?

728
01:09:17,586 --> 01:09:18,712
lnstead of shooting at the target

729
01:09:18,921 --> 01:09:20,411
...he shot sideways during training

730
01:09:20,623 --> 01:09:21,089
Yes

731
01:09:21,357 --> 01:09:22,085
He is too casual

732
01:09:22,458 --> 01:09:22,947
l`m very serious

733
01:09:23,025 --> 01:09:23,650
l don`t think so. l think
you were just casual

734
01:09:23,859 --> 01:09:24,348
He`s making trouble everywhere

735
01:09:24,426 --> 01:09:25,859
...and was scolded by the instructors

736
01:09:26,395 --> 01:09:27,987
Why don`t you tell his stories?

737
01:09:29,098 --> 01:09:30,122
We were all scolded...

738
01:09:30,332 --> 01:09:33,665
By Joe and Bill

739
01:09:33,836 --> 01:09:34,768
Bill! Bill!

740
01:09:34,904 --> 01:09:36,462
lt is you who said this

741
01:09:37,006 --> 01:09:39,338
l don`t want to talk about Bill

742
01:09:39,508 --> 01:09:40,532
But you`ve said it

743
01:09:40,743 --> 01:09:41,471
Yeah

744
01:09:41,844 --> 01:09:42,776
And now l can scold anyone

745
01:09:42,978 --> 01:09:43,740
...instead of being scolded

746
01:09:43,946 --> 01:09:44,605
lt`s a pity you weren`t here just now

747
01:09:44,680 --> 01:09:45,647
0h yeah, how`s that?

748
01:09:45,881 --> 01:09:48,782
Run faster

749
01:09:50,052 --> 01:09:50,711
Even if someone runs well...

750
01:09:51,020 --> 01:09:52,282
l will still say he isn`t good enough

751
01:09:53,689 --> 01:09:55,179
Are you thirsty?

752
01:09:55,891 --> 01:09:56,755
Yeah, we are thirsty

753
01:09:56,992 --> 01:09:57,754
What should we drink?

754
01:09:57,960 --> 01:09:58,949
Your treat

755
01:09:59,161 --> 01:09:59,991
0kay

756
01:10:00,196 --> 01:10:02,027
So, let`s go

757
01:10:02,331 --> 01:10:03,491
Go quickly

758
01:10:03,999 --> 01:10:05,626
Stone, are you really leaving?

759
01:10:05,834 --> 01:10:07,893
Are you going to leave all
these naughty boys to us?

760
01:10:09,471 --> 01:10:10,768
This is my last chance

761
01:10:11,006 --> 01:10:12,769
You should know Ann

762
01:10:13,075 --> 01:10:14,872
lf l don`t get married this time

763
01:10:15,077 --> 01:10:16,408
l will be single for the rest of my life

764
01:10:16,612 --> 01:10:19,046
You shouldn`t abandon
the whole forest for one tree

765
01:10:19,348 --> 01:10:22,715
No, Sir! 0f course

766
01:10:22,918 --> 01:10:25,113
l know what are on their minds

767
01:10:25,287 --> 01:10:28,450
A few years ago, we were like them

768
01:10:28,624 --> 01:10:32,651
But we were better physically

769
01:10:32,828 --> 01:10:35,797
l don`t believe some people
are born heroes

770
01:10:35,998 --> 01:10:38,831
J ust spend six months training them

771
01:10:39,301 --> 01:10:41,531
...and they will come out right!

772
01:10:41,737 --> 01:10:46,401
We should give them a chance!

773
01:10:46,609 --> 01:10:48,372
Hey, you are right

774
01:10:48,744 --> 01:10:51,645
You sound very mature

775
01:10:51,847 --> 01:10:55,476
l don`t believe that one can be lucky

776
01:10:55,684 --> 01:10:57,345
...or unlucky all his life

777
01:10:57,553 --> 01:10:58,383
Take me as an example

778
01:11:00,289 --> 01:11:02,052
l was paralyzed a few months ago, now

779
01:11:02,458 --> 01:11:03,720
...l can walk, and l am an instructor
in the SDU

780
01:11:04,360 --> 01:11:07,818
All because you give me a chance

781
01:11:08,030 --> 01:11:10,055
So l think we should give t
he new blood a chance

782
01:11:10,332 --> 01:11:12,357
Stone, look! What is this?

783
01:11:12,868 --> 01:11:13,664
Goose skin

784
01:11:14,370 --> 01:11:18,670
But he sounds quite sensible
quite mature

785
01:11:19,508 --> 01:11:20,839
l won`t consider leaving the SDU

786
01:11:21,844 --> 01:11:24,244
...a few years ago

787
01:11:24,446 --> 01:11:26,573
But now this guy is more mature

788
01:11:26,749 --> 01:11:29,149
l think l can go now

789
01:11:29,351 --> 01:11:29,874
You are right

790
01:11:30,085 --> 01:11:30,881
Lucky Lun

791
01:11:33,022 --> 01:11:34,683
Someone you desperately want
to meet has come

792
01:11:35,124 --> 01:11:36,853
l don`t want to see anyone now

793
01:11:37,026 --> 01:11:39,085
You must want to see this person

794
01:11:39,295 --> 01:11:41,195
Who is it?

795
01:11:42,164 --> 01:11:43,756
l`ll go with you

796
01:11:44,199 --> 01:11:44,824
This person really wants to see me

797
01:11:45,034 --> 01:11:45,966
Sure

798
01:11:46,168 --> 01:11:47,328
Then go

799
01:11:47,936 --> 01:11:50,734
Yeah, go quickly

800
01:11:50,806 --> 01:11:51,704
This coffee is really good

801
01:11:52,107 --> 01:11:52,903
Yes, where did you get it?

802
01:11:53,075 --> 01:11:53,939
J ust across the street

803
01:11:55,144 --> 01:11:56,543
This lame man

804
01:11:56,745 --> 01:11:57,803
What are they doing?

805
01:11:58,547 --> 01:11:59,605
You need to get a wife

806
01:11:59,782 --> 01:12:01,750
They are young. They need to meet girls

807
01:12:03,852 --> 01:12:04,784
Ah Yee

808
01:12:05,487 --> 01:12:06,181
Hey

809
01:12:06,388 --> 01:12:07,150
Wow!

810
01:12:07,356 --> 01:12:08,380
What happened to your leg?

811
01:12:08,757 --> 01:12:09,951
You two have a chat

812
01:12:11,860 --> 01:12:13,589
When did you return to Hong Kong?

813
01:12:14,229 --> 01:12:15,287
l have returned for two days

814
01:12:15,497 --> 01:12:18,591
How did you get hurt?

815
01:12:20,636 --> 01:12:23,161
ln an operation. l am okay now

816
01:12:23,372 --> 01:12:24,839
Almost completely recovered

817
01:12:25,507 --> 01:12:27,202
See, l can even run a bit now

818
01:12:29,278 --> 01:12:30,836
0kay, l believe you

819
01:12:31,046 --> 01:12:32,206
Let me hold your arms

820
01:12:35,084 --> 01:12:39,418
l`ve heard about the tragedy
of your girl friend

821
01:12:41,190 --> 01:12:43,283
Sorry, l shouldn`t ask

822
01:12:43,892 --> 01:12:46,759
Let bygones be bygones

823
01:12:46,962 --> 01:12:48,589
l had some happy times with her

824
01:12:48,764 --> 01:12:49,731
...and some unhappy times

825
01:12:49,898 --> 01:12:51,229
lt is all over now

826
01:12:51,600 --> 01:12:53,033
l still have to lead my life

827
01:12:54,036 --> 01:12:55,401
Sit down

828
01:12:55,871 --> 01:12:56,462
Here

829
01:12:56,672 --> 01:13:09,517
Grab it. This thing is getting in my way

830
01:13:14,890 --> 01:13:15,857
When will you leave?

831
01:13:17,526 --> 01:13:18,458
l won`t go back

832
01:13:18,627 --> 01:13:19,594
Why

833
01:13:20,562 --> 01:13:23,326
Beijing is too big. l love Hong Kong

834
01:13:23,532 --> 01:13:25,397
lt is smaller and more convenient

835
01:13:26,001 --> 01:13:27,127
Traffic is convenient

836
01:13:28,504 --> 01:13:29,732
Yeah, quite

837
01:13:30,038 --> 01:13:31,699
Did you make new friends?

838
01:13:31,907 --> 01:13:34,205
Yeah, many

839
01:13:34,476 --> 01:13:36,239
Especially boys?

840
01:13:37,045 --> 01:13:44,952
No, l find their accents hard to learn

841
01:13:45,154 --> 01:13:48,180
When they say anything

842
01:13:48,357 --> 01:13:54,057
...they always add an ``r`` to the end
of the word

843
01:13:54,396 --> 01:13:55,920
Like lunchrr instead of lunch

844
01:13:56,165 --> 01:13:59,032
So l like Hong Kong boys more!

845
01:13:59,334 --> 01:14:00,631
But don`t you love their tongues

846
01:14:00,836 --> 01:14:03,464
...which can roll all the ``r``s?

847
01:14:08,010 --> 01:14:11,070
You haven`t changed

848
01:14:12,014 --> 01:14:14,005
No, l am just joking

849
01:14:14,249 --> 01:14:16,046
Can`t you be more serious?

850
01:14:16,985 --> 01:14:18,316
l do hope that you have changed

851
01:14:18,487 --> 01:14:19,511
...but you are still the same

852
01:14:19,721 --> 01:14:21,882
He`s more serious now

853
01:14:22,791 --> 01:14:23,587
How do you know?

854
01:14:23,792 --> 01:14:25,987
0f course l know. l am always with him

855
01:14:31,166 --> 01:14:34,260
Ah Yee, can we...

856
01:14:34,436 --> 01:14:35,425
Sure

857
01:14:35,637 --> 01:14:36,604
Do you know what l am
going to ask her?

858
01:14:37,806 --> 01:14:46,009
You want to ask her if you two
could be friends, right?

859
01:14:47,983 --> 01:14:50,508
0h yes, maybe even go steady

860
01:14:54,990 --> 01:14:56,014
Can we?

861
01:14:59,795 --> 01:15:01,126
l`ll take you back

862
01:15:02,531 --> 01:15:10,302
Good, can l kiss a friend?

863
01:15:11,974 --> 01:15:13,100
Let me hold you

864
01:15:41,036 --> 01:15:42,936
lf Hon Gin hadn`t taken the wrong step

865
01:15:43,138 --> 01:15:44,833
l am sure he would be a good cop

866
01:15:46,241 --> 01:15:49,472
Hon had made many mistakes

867
01:15:49,678 --> 01:15:52,078
...but he was a good man

868
01:15:52,281 --> 01:15:55,546
Even if he was not a cop

869
01:15:56,518 --> 01:16:01,979
You are right. But l feel sorry for Piano

870
01:16:03,125 --> 01:16:04,456
When people fall in love

871
01:16:04,893 --> 01:16:09,057
...they accept everything
about his partner

872
01:16:09,464 --> 01:16:13,901
Piano truly loved Hon!

873
01:16:16,371 --> 01:16:17,895
lt`s perhaps romantic

874
01:16:18,106 --> 01:16:19,937
...to die for the one you love

875
01:16:20,142 --> 01:16:21,404
...though it`s not rational

876
01:16:21,610 --> 01:16:22,804
Do you agree?

877
01:16:24,813 --> 01:16:25,780
Maybe

878
01:16:26,748 --> 01:16:29,945
l always tell Kim what happens to you

879
01:16:30,152 --> 01:16:31,084
Do you?

880
01:16:31,720 --> 01:16:33,517
We are good friends

881
01:16:33,889 --> 01:16:36,016
Since we will soon go to the States

882
01:16:36,258 --> 01:16:37,486
...let`s go and visit her grave

883
01:16:37,659 --> 01:16:38,921
No problem

884
01:16:39,628 --> 01:16:42,119
ln fact, l have arranged everything

885
01:16:42,331 --> 01:16:43,320
Let`s go get the flowers

886
01:16:44,266 --> 01:16:46,063
You have arranged everything?

887
01:16:46,234 --> 01:16:48,361
0f course, so there will be no excuse

888
01:16:50,772 --> 01:16:53,036
Cousin, don`t you feel a bit strange?

889
01:16:53,241 --> 01:16:54,139
What`s the matter?

890
01:16:54,443 --> 01:16:55,705
You are getting married tomorrow

891
01:16:55,911 --> 01:16:57,105
...and leave for the States

892
01:16:57,312 --> 01:16:57,971
...but you are packing your luggage

893
01:16:58,213 --> 01:16:59,407
...alone at home all by yourself!

894
01:17:00,115 --> 01:17:01,446
We are like that

895
01:17:01,650 --> 01:17:03,208
Each minds his own business

896
01:17:04,052 --> 01:17:06,782
But, don`t you think this isn`t right?

897
01:17:06,989 --> 01:17:09,287
What the hell is he doing in the camp?

898
01:17:10,158 --> 01:17:12,524
Probably nothing

899
01:17:14,296 --> 01:17:15,160
Really?

900
01:17:20,068 --> 01:17:21,035
Hey

901
01:17:21,269 --> 01:17:22,099
Are you packing?

902
01:17:22,504 --> 01:17:23,937
Yeah, and you?

903
01:17:24,106 --> 01:17:25,573
l don`t have much to pack

904
01:17:26,108 --> 01:17:28,872
Tomorrow, you come to the camp
to pick me up

905
01:17:29,778 --> 01:17:30,710
0kay

906
01:17:30,979 --> 01:17:32,412
l won`t bother you now. Bye

907
01:17:32,581 --> 01:17:33,275
Bye

908
01:17:34,716 --> 01:17:35,614
Who is it? ls that him?

909
01:17:35,817 --> 01:17:36,681
Yes

910
01:17:38,453 --> 01:17:40,512
What did he say?

911
01:17:40,722 --> 01:17:42,280
He asked me to pick him up tomorrow

912
01:17:43,091 --> 01:17:44,319
l know what is wrong!

913
01:17:44,526 --> 01:17:45,185
You have reversed your roles

914
01:17:45,394 --> 01:17:47,555
You act like a man and he
acts like a woman

915
01:17:47,763 --> 01:17:49,355
You have to pick him up tomorrow

916
01:17:52,567 --> 01:17:53,966
lt pisses me off

917
01:18:08,016 --> 01:18:09,950
Attention

918
01:18:10,185 --> 01:18:11,049
Directionless Mo

919
01:18:12,287 --> 01:18:13,151
Sir

920
01:18:14,423 --> 01:18:22,194
Thank you. You are the best of the best

921
01:18:22,998 --> 01:18:25,023
l enjoy working with you

922
01:18:25,834 --> 01:18:28,496
Thanks for your courage and efforts

923
01:18:28,704 --> 01:18:31,537
Keep up the good traditions of the SDU

924
01:18:32,340 --> 01:18:33,830
Wish you all good luck

925
01:18:38,013 --> 01:18:48,947
Take care. You too, Joe. Take care

926
01:18:50,025 --> 01:18:51,856
0kay, take your time

927
01:19:14,349 --> 01:19:15,782
You must remember this place

928
01:19:17,085 --> 01:19:20,054
Yes, there are many
good memories here

929
01:19:21,456 --> 01:19:26,120
Bill, Hon Gin, Jesu, Lucky Lun
Directionless Mo

930
01:19:27,462 --> 01:19:33,264
l was here everyday, teaching them

931
01:19:33,468 --> 01:19:35,163
l also thought about you while l was here

932
01:19:35,403 --> 01:19:37,234
...so you are also in my memory

933
01:19:40,609 --> 01:19:42,338
l think you should stay

934
01:19:42,677 --> 01:19:45,475
What are you saying?

935
01:19:46,081 --> 01:19:48,140
We have arranged everything

936
01:19:48,917 --> 01:19:50,350
0ur entire luggage is here

937
01:19:52,554 --> 01:19:53,612
Don`t you know that you will be unhappy

938
01:19:53,889 --> 01:19:56,255
...if you come with me to the States?

939
01:19:58,693 --> 01:19:59,921
l am a foreigner in Hong Kong

940
01:20:00,228 --> 01:20:01,855
l will feel more at ease in the States...

941
01:20:02,063 --> 01:20:03,792
Even more at ease with you by my side

942
01:20:04,599 --> 01:20:07,295
l don`t think so. You are not a foreigner

943
01:20:07,536 --> 01:20:10,369
You are more conservative than me

944
01:20:10,572 --> 01:20:11,539
Really?

945
01:20:12,974 --> 01:20:14,771
ln fact, it means a lot

946
01:20:15,076 --> 01:20:16,805
...when you gave me this ring

947
01:20:17,746 --> 01:20:18,713
Thank you

948
01:20:27,823 --> 01:20:29,484
l want to go with you

949
01:20:29,658 --> 01:20:32,855
You will be bored if you go alone

950
01:20:33,061 --> 01:20:35,689
No, l won`t. l have to study

951
01:20:35,897 --> 01:20:37,592
l will think of you when l have time

952
01:20:37,799 --> 01:20:38,288
Really?

953
01:20:38,500 --> 01:20:45,929
You stay! l am leaving now

954
01:24:42,377 --> 01:24:43,173
Sir

955
01:24:43,711 --> 01:24:44,541
Lucky Lun, how are you?

956
01:24:45,213 --> 01:24:46,237
Getting fatter and fatter

957
01:24:47,115 --> 01:24:47,979
How`s your leg?

958
01:24:48,183 --> 01:24:49,673
l can run like them

959
01:24:51,086 --> 01:24:52,053
Are they running?

960
01:24:52,253 --> 01:24:54,153
l don`t think so. They are just walking!

961
01:24:54,389 --> 01:24:55,549
l agree

962
01:24:56,157 --> 01:24:57,089
What the hell are you doing?

963
01:24:57,325 --> 01:24:58,792
Walking or running?

964
01:25:04,766 --> 01:25:05,494
Welcome back

965
01:25:05,900 --> 01:25:11,861
l have thought it over for a long time

966
01:25:12,073 --> 01:25:13,665
l don`t think l can leave now because

967
01:25:14,008 --> 01:25:16,374
...you are still not mature enough

968
01:25:17,445 --> 01:25:18,309
What happened?

969
01:25:19,414 --> 01:25:20,779
What about this training?

970
01:25:21,182 --> 01:25:22,114
Still want to run?

971
01:25:22,383 --> 01:25:23,145
Yes, Sir

972
01:25:23,351 --> 01:25:24,181
Do you want some training?

973
01:25:24,419 --> 01:25:25,317
Yes, Sir

974
01:25:25,487 --> 01:25:28,650
0kay, let`s do it

